      <section>
      <p>I am a Bare-Metal Applications Engineer at <a href="http://www.qualcomm.co.in/">Qualcomm</a> in Bangalore. I graduated from <a href="https://https://www.iitm.ac.in/">IIT Madras</a> with a Bachelor's in Electrical Engineering and a Masters in VLSI Design. The focus of my work at Qualcomm is to evaluate Thermal Mitigation Algorithms without software stack operating on the hardware.</p>

        <p>While at IIT I was interested in Applied Mathematics, which I try to pursue by working on several personal projects</p>

